skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: uwu voice
des: UWU Voice is an entertaining Alexa skill that converts any text you provide into the whimsical "uwu" speech style, characterized by playful word alterations and pronunciation changes. Perfect for sharing lighthearted moments with friends and family, UWU Voice will add a touch of fun to your Alexa experience. To use the skill, simply ask Alexa to say your desired phrase in uwu style, and let the fun begin!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
